# This directory is the default `DATA_DIR` for `docker compose up` when
# no override is set in .env. It exists so that the out-of-the-box
# experience works without manual `mkdir -p`.
#
# For PRODUCTION validators you should NOT use this in-repo path —
# point DATA_DIR at something stable like /opt/connito/data so your
# checkpoints survive a `git clean`, a re-clone, or a repo move.
#
# Ignore everything inside this tree except the skeleton itself, so we
# never accidentally commit checkpoints, wallets, wandb runs, or HF
# downloads.

*
!.gitignore
!*/
!*/.gitkeep
!configs/validator.example.yaml
